    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Rasjid Chan</b>\n</p><p><b>Rasjid Chan</b>, <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br />\na Singaporean chess programmer with passion for <a href=\"/Bit-Twiddling\" title=\"Bit-Twiddling\">bit-twiddling</a> and <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboards</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nRasjid is author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible chess programs <a href=\"/SnailChess\" title=\"SnailChess\">SnailChess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Cowrie_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Cowrie Chess (page does not exist)\">Cowrie Chess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rasjid_Chan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rasjid_Chan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=31555\">SnailChess-new release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 03, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=33767\">SnailChess Copper, a new re-write</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 12, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=37851\">SnailChess Copper Revived- Ver 4.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 21, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=358468\">Hashing is a complicated affair&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 05, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=359243\">sliding attacks in three #define</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 09, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Sliding_Piece_Attacks\" title=\"Sliding Piece Attacks\">Sliding Piece Attacks</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rasjid_Chan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=2101\">Does simple futility prune work</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 27, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=432374\">Hashing double bounds</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 20, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6573#p30811\">Re: Bitboard of squares between</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 15, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Square_Attacked_By#InBetween\" title=\"Square Attacked By\">In Between Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16784\">Hashing and mate scores</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 29, 2007</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rasjid_Chan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34025\">Does perft include underpromotion?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34365\">A hashing problem</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 18, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40145\">Fruit-Rybka and Copyrights</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 22, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=480202&amp;t=44899\">Re: how to make a chess interface</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 27, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47330\">SEE</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 25, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47477\">My program can't mate KQK or KRK!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 11, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47557\">How to implement KPK&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 21, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/KPK\" title=\"KPK\">KPK</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=48274&amp;start=1\">Re: First post (and FailHigh question!)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 14, 2013</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rasjid_Chan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Chan Rasjid in <a href=\"/Big-endian\" title=\"Big-endian\">Big-endian</a> Asian standard template [LAST NAME][FIRST NAME]</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6573#p30811\">Re: Bitboard of squares between</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rasjid Chan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 15, 2007</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"ref